ZH: 我们在山冈上看到了一只小松鼠。
EN: We saw a small squirrel on the hill.

ZH: 山冈上的树木郁郁葱葱，非常美丽。
EN: The trees on the hill are lush and very beautiful.

ZH: 这座山冈是我们家族的传统聚会地点。
EN: This hill is the traditional gathering place for our family.

ZH: 夏天的山冈上常常吹着凉爽的风。
EN: The hill often has a cool breeze blowing in the summer.

ZH: 我喜欢在山冈上散步，享受大自然的美景。
EN: I love walking on the hill and enjoying the beauty of nature.

