EN: There is an ancient temple on the hill.

ZH: 山冈是我们家四代人的家园。
EN: The hill is the home of four generations of our family.

ZH: 在山冈上，我们可以看到整个城市的景色。
EN: On the hill, we can see the entire cityscape.

ZH: 我们拿着野餐篮子去山冈野餐。
EN: We took a picnic basket to the hill for a picnic.

